{"tid":632648,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★iPhone X殺手---Android之父打造Essential Phone 價格累劈近半","createTime":"2018-04-17T14:55:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T14:31:57.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"dade3ab81fcd6231919463872cd79603aed10877","tid":632648,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T14:55:26.000Z","msg":"由Android之父魯賓(Andy Rubin)打造的Essential Phone，一度被市場譽為iPhone X殺手，但奈何發布至今逾半年時間，作為首批全面屏的智能手機，84.9%的屏幕佔比，卻無法吸引消費者，售價接連劈至399.99美元清貨。<br />\n<br />\n外媒報道指，在外國大型零售連銷店百思賣上，Essential Phone售價再一次調整，從499.99美元降低到399.99美元（約3,199.9港元）。<br />\n<br />\n要知道，Essential開售時可是要價699.99美元，現在幾乎是半價發售。<br />\n<br />\n配置方面，Essential Phone搭載高通驍龍835處理器，配備4GB內存+128GB內置存儲，5.7吋1440P分辨率屏幕，屏幕為19:10比例，電池容量3040mAh，系統已經升級到Android 8.1。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180417/bkn-20180417214930981-0417_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180417%2Fbkn-20180417214930981-0417_00842_001.html&d=kJKF5bKJ3bb1eMIg7r1iL9ZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=1554711c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180417/bkn-20180417214930981-0417_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b1e3842919bfa3ed7a88e4e5a245f37a4619a5f8","tid":632648,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T14:55:40.000Z","msg":"apple need die<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9048e1ee3a5043735e2c68dccc00d0c0a5f8487c","tid":632648,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1e3842919bfa3ed7a88e4e5a245f37a4619a5f8","tid":632648,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T14:55:40.000Z","msg":"apple need die<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T15:35:44.000Z","msg":"有你去買，點會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5742ae165cff6dc